  "hashtags": ["#PCBDesign", "#PCBChecklist", "#DesignForManufacturing", "#DFM", "#ElectronicsDesign", "#CuCircuits", "#HardwareEngineering", "#MakeInIndia"],
  "caption": "Stop. Before you send that Gerber file, run through this checklist.\n\nWe see it every week at Cu Circuits: boards that come back with avoidable errors. Wrong trace widths. Missing decoupling caps. Silkscreen over pads. Drill holes too close to the edge.\n\nThese are not complex problems. They are checklist problems.\n\nHere are 10 critical checks every hardware engineer should run before hitting 'Order PCB.' Save this post. Print it. Tape it to your monitor.\n\nBecause a $5 checklist review today saves a $500 respin next week.\n\nWhich check do you most often forget? Drop it in the comments.\n\n#PCBDesign #PCBChecklist #DesignForManufacturing #DFM #ElectronicsDesign #CuCircuits #HardwareEngineering #MakeInIndia",
  "strategy": {"format": "checklist_scorecard", "visual_approach": "green checkmarks and priority badges with category grouping"},
  "html": "<div style=\"width:1080px; height:1350px; background:#0a0a0a; position:relative; overflow:hidden; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing:border-box;\">\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,102,68,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,102,68,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 54px 54px;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:3px; background:#006644;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:40px; left:48px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px;\">\n    <div style=\"width:36px; height:36px; background:#006644; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Cu</span>\n    </div>\n    <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Design Review</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:100px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:160px; font-weight:900; color:#006644; line-height:0.9; letter-spacing:-8px;\">80%+</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:12px; letter-spacing:1px;\">of PCB errors caught with this checklist</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:320px; left:48px; width:80px; height:3px; background:#006644;\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:346px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\">Electrical</div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Run DRC with zero errors before export</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Verify trace widths for current capacity</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Decoupling caps on every IC (100nF near VCC)</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">LVS check: layout matches schematic exactly</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:620px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\">Mechanical</div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Board outline and mounting holes verified</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Drill sizes and annular rings per fab spec</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:808px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\">Manufacturing</div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Silkscreen clear of all solderable pads</div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:10px 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:14px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Test points accessible for debug probing</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:80px; left:48px; right:48px; display:flex; gap:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(204,51,51,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Avg Respin Cost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#cc3333; margin-top:4px;\">$2,500</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(184,110,0,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Time Lost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#b86e00; margin-top:4px;\">2 Weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(0,102,68,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Errors Caught</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#006644; margin-top:4px;\">80%+</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:28px; left:48px; right:48px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);\">cucircuits.com</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Source: Altium, Cadence PCB Design Resources</div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
